					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 23
					39 00 00 00 00 00 15 C1 0E FF EE FF FF EE FF FF EE FF FF EE FF FF EE FF FF FF 7F FF
					//OP P1 VGL EN
					39 00 00 40 00 00 06 F0 55 AA 52 08 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 10
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 B5 00 71 71 71 71 71 00 00 18 2B 00 00 00 18 2B 00
					39 00 00 40 00 00 06 F0 55 AA 52 08 05
					39 00 00 40 00 00 0A C4 02 00 82 AA 00 00 70 00 00
					//op P1
					39 00 00 40 00 00 06 F0 55 AA 52 08 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 1C
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 01 01 01 01 01 01 00 00 01 01 00 00 00 00 00 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 2C
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 01 01 01 01 01 03 01 01 01 03 01 01 00 00 00 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 3C
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 01 01 01 01 01 04 03 03 01 04 03 03 00 00 00 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 4C
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 01 01 01 01 01 04 03 0B 01 04 03 0B 00 00 00 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 5C
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01 01
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 6C
					39 00 00 40 00 00 09 BA 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00
					//qsync supported modify
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 74
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 00 01 02 03 04 05 07 09 0B 77 EF 00 03 77 0B 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 84
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 00 01 02 03 04 05 07 09 0B 77 EF 00 03 77 0B 00
					15 00 00 40 00 00 02 6F 94
					39 00 00 40 00 00 11 BA 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00
